Anyone interested in Japanese Swordsmanship is welcome,

to join us. Esaka Senseis' visit is the first of what we hope will be
many to the San Francisco Bay Area. If you have any questions feel
free to email me off-list or contact Andrej thru the website.
your friend in the way,
Tom
